It was the deadliest earthquake to hit China since the 1976 Tangshan earthquake , which killed at least 240,000 people , and the strongest in the country since the 1950 Chayu earthquake , which registered at 8.5 on the Richter magnitude scale .
It is the 21st deadliest earthquake of all time .
Starting from Wenchuan , the rupture propagated at an average speed of 3.1 kilometers per second 49 ° toward north east , rupturing a total of about 300 km .
Geng , while acknowledging that earthquake prediction was broadly considered problematic by the scientific community , believed that `` the bigger the earthquake , the easier it is to predict . ''
The same Yazhou Zhoukan article pointed out the inherent difficulties associated with predicting earthquakes .
In response , an official with the Seismological Bureau stated that `` earthquake prediction is widely acknowledged around the world to be difficult from a scientific standpoint . ''
According to reports from Chengdu , the capital of Sichuan province , the earthquake tremors lasted for `` about two or three minutes '' .
The Yingxiu liedu-XI zone is about 66 km long and 20 km wide along Wenchuan -- Dujiangyan -- Pengzhou ; the Beichuan liedu-XI zone is about 82 km long and 15 km wide along An County -- Beichuan -- Pingwu .
The area with liedu X -LRB- comparable to X on EMS , `` destructive '' and X on MM , `` disastrous '' -RRB- spans 3,144 km2 .
The area affected by earthquakes exceeding liedu VI totals 440,442 km2 , occupying an oval 936 km long and 596 km wide , spanning three provinces and one autonomous region .
This earthquake ruptured at least two imbricate structures in Longmen Shan Fault System , i.e. the Beichuan Fault and the Guanxian -- Anxian Fault .
One SilkAir flight was diverted and landed in Kunming as a result .
The Juyuan Middle School , where many teenagers were buried , was excavated by civilians and cranes .
Dujiangyan is home of the Dujiangyan Irrigation System , an ancient water diversion project which is still in use and is a UNESCO World Heritage Site .
The project 's famous Fish Mouth was cracked but not severely damaged otherwise .
Nonetheless , the well-being of an even greater number of pandas in the neighbouring panda reserves remained unknown .
Five security guards at the reserve were killed by the earthquake .
By May 20 , two pandas at the reserve were found to be injured , while the search continued for another two adult pandas that went missing after the quake .
By May 28 , 2008 , one panda was still missing .
The missing panda was later found dead under the rubble of an enclosure .
Panda keepers and other workers placed her remains in a small wooden crate and buried her outside the breeding centre .
The old county seat of Beichuan was abandoned and preserved as part of the Beichuan Earthquake Museum .
A 56-year-old was killed in Dujiangyan during a rescue attempt on the Lingyanshan Ropeway , where due to the earthquake 11 tourists from Taiwan had been trapped inside cable cars since May 13 .
A 4-year-old boy named Zhu Shaowei -LRB- traditional Chinese : 朱紹維 ; simplified Chinese : 朱绍维 ; pinyin : Zhū Shàowéi -RRB- was also killed in Mianzhu City when a house collapsed on him and another was reported missing .
Another 700 students were buried in a school in Hanwang .
Up to 1,300 children and teachers died at Beichuan Middle School .
Catastrophe modeling firm AIR Worldwide reported official estimates of insurers ' losses at US$ 1 billion from the earthquake ; estimated total damages exceed US$ 20 billion .
It values Chengdu , at the time having an urban population of 4.5 million people , at around US$ 115 billion , with only a small portion covered by insurance .
DesRoches said : `` If the buildings were older and built prior to that 1976 earthquake , chances are they were n't built for adequate earthquake forces . ''
Strong aftershocks continued to strike even months after the main quake .
The same area suffered two more aftershocks of 5.6 and 6.0 Ms -LRB- 5.8 and 5.5 Mw , respectively , according to USGS -RRB- on July 23 , resulting in 1 death , 6 serious injuries , collapse of hundreds of homes and damaging kilometers of highways .
Pingwu County and Beichuan County , Sichuan , also northeast of Wenchuan and close to the epicenter of a 7.2 Ms earthquake in 1976 , suffered a 6.1 Ms aftershock -LRB- 5.7 Mw according to USGS -RRB- on August 1 ; it caused 2 deaths , 345 injuries , collapse of 707 homes , damages to over 1,000 homes , and blocked 25 kilometres -LRB- 16 mi -RRB- of country roads .
The government spent $ 441 billion on relief and reconstruction efforts .
General Secretary and President Hu Jintao announced that the disaster response would be rapid .
