He based his study on statistical correlation .
That Sichuan is a seismically active area has been discussed for years prior to the quake , though few studies point to a specific date and time .
The 1,300 rescuers reached the epicenter , and 300 pioneer troops reached the seat of Wenchuan at about 23:30 CST .
By 12:17 CST , May 14 , 2008 , communication in the seat of Wenchuan was partly revived .
