Tzu Chi was the first force from outside the People 's Republic of China to join the rescue effort .
No-one survived .
Due to the one-child policy , many families lost their only child when schools in the region collapsed during the earthquake .
Consequently , Sichuan provincial and local officials have lifted the restriction for families whose only child was either killed or severely injured in the disaster .
