West 's first six solo studio albums , all of which have gone platinum , have received numerous awards and critical acclaim .
Billboard ranked Kanye West No. 3 on their list of Top 10 Producers of the Decade .
West 's outspoken views and ventures outside of music have received significant mainstream attention .
He has been a frequent source of controversy and public scrutiny for his conduct at award shows , on social media , and in other public settings .
Tibetan Buddhism , which preserves the Vajrayana teachings of eighth century India , is practiced in regions surrounding the Himalayas , Mongolia and Kalmykia .
Buddhist schools vary on the exact nature of the path to liberation , the importance and canonicity of various teachings and scriptures , and especially their respective practices .
Taking `` refuge in the triple gem '' has traditionally been a declaration and commitment to being on the Buddhist path , and in general distinguishes a Buddhist from a non-Buddhist .
Scholars are hesitant to make unqualified claims about the historical facts of the Buddha 's life .
