They also emphasized Theravada being rational and scientific .
Theravāda is primarily practiced today in Sri Lanka , Burma , Laos , Thailand , Cambodia as well as small portions of China , Vietnam , Malaysia and Bangladesh .
Monks follow the vinaya : meditating , teaching and serving their lay communities .
Mahayana Buddhism flourished in India from the 5th century CE onwards , during the dynasty of the Guptas .
