Schwarzenegger served in the Austrian Army in 1965 to fulfill the one year of service required at the time of all 18-year-old Austrian males .
He went AWOL during basic training so he could take part in the competition and spent a week in military prison : `` Participating in the competition meant so much to me that I did n't carefully think through the consequences . ''
